{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Wood Rooster|kanji=乙酉|romaji=kinoto tori|onyomi=otsuyu|p=yǐyǒu|w=i-yu|mi=i²¹ i̯ɤʊ̯²¹|y=jyut6 jau5|j=jyut6 jau5|ci=jyt̚ jɐu|mc=ʔit jɨu|oc-bs=Ɂik jɯʔ}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yin Wood Rooster also known as 乙酉''' (kino totori, otsuboku no tori, itsuyuu) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
It is the 22nd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申|1=Yang Wood Monkey|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Boushoku|ja|丙戌|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} symbol {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Wood|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}} symbol {{ill|Rooster|ja|酉|1=Rooster (zodiac)|2=ja|3=酉|4=fr|5=Coq (astrologie chinoise)|6=nl|7=Haan (astrologie)|lt=Rooster (酉)|1=Rooster (zodiac)|lt=Rooster (酉)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Metal|ja|金|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) (i.e. Metal overcomes Wood).
==Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s Years== A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 25 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of {{ill|Otsuyuu|ja|乙酉|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s years table''' |- ! {{ill|1st Millennium|ja|1千年紀|qq=draft|qq=draft}} !! {{ill|2nd Millennium|ja|2千年紀|qq=draft|qq=draft}} !! {{ill|3rd Millennium|ja|3千年紀|qq=draft|qq=draft}} |- | * [[25]] * [[85]] * [[145]] * [[205]] * [[265]] * [[325]] * [[385]] * [[445]] * [[505]] * [[565]] * [[625]] * [[685]] * [[745]] * [[805]] * [[865]] * [[925]] * [[985]] | * [[1045]] * [[1105]] * [[1165]] * [[1225]] * [[1285]] * [[1345]] * [[1405]] * [[1465]] * [[1525]] * [[1585]] * [[1645]] * [[1705]] * [[1765]] * [[1825]] * [[1885]] * [[1945]] | * [[2005]] * [[2065]] * [[2125]] * [[2185]] * [[2245]] * [[2305]] * [[2365]] * [[2425]] * [[2485]] * [[2545]] * [[2605]] * [[2665]] * [[2725]] * [[2785]] * [[2845]] * [[2905]] * [[2965]] |}
==Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s Months== In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}), the month of {{ill|August|ja|8月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of {{ill|Otsuyuu|ja|乙酉|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (from {{ill|White Dew|ja|白露|qq=draft|qq=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|寒露|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) as applicable.
==Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft}} for {{ill|Otsuyuu|ja|乙酉|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is as follows. ==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu}}=== 乙酉の日 is the 2nd day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijou|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
