==Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s Years== A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} that leaves a remainder of 25 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/year|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/year|qq=}} of {{ill|Otsuyuu|ja|1=Yin Wood Rooster|2=ja|乙酉|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s years table''' |- ! {{ill|1st Millennium|ja|1千年紀|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1st Millennium|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1st Millennium|qq=}} !! {{ill|2nd Millennium|ja|2千年紀|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2nd Millennium|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2nd Millennium|qq=}} !! {{ill|3rd Millennium|ja|3千年紀|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/3rd Millennium|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/3rd Millennium|qq=}} |- | * [[25]] * [[85]] * [[145]] * [[205]] * [[265]] * [[325]] * [[385]] * [[445]] * [[505]] * [[565]] * [[625]] * [[685]] * [[745]] * [[805]] * [[865]] * [[925]] * [[985]] | * [[1045]] * [[1105]] * [[1165]] * [[1225]] * [[1285]] * [[1345]] * [[1405]] * [[1465]] * [[1525]] * [[1585]] * [[1645]] * [[1705]] * [[1765]] * [[1825]] * [[1885]] * [[1945]] | * [[2005]] * [[2065]] * [[2125]] * [[2185]] * [[2245]] * [[2305]] * [[2365]] * [[2425]] * [[2485]] * [[2545]] * [[2605]] * [[2665]] * [[2725]] * [[2785]] * [[2845]] * [[2905]] * [[2965]] |}
==Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s Months== In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|lt=Kinoto (乙)|2=ja|3=乙|4=zh|5=乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|August|ja|8月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/August|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/August|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Otsuyuu|ja|1=Yin Wood Rooster|2=ja|乙酉|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|White Dew|ja|白露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/White Dew|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/White Dew|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|寒露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Cold|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Cold|qq=}}) as applicable.
==Yin Wood Rooster (乙酉)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Otsuyuu|ja|1=Yin Wood Rooster|2=ja|乙酉|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=}} is as follows. ==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu|qq=}}=== 乙酉の日 is the 2nd day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijou|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten Ichijou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten Ichijou|qq=}}.
